ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="c80cad3c-fc87-467f-a9a6-f1e00fd45ef2" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="DMI and AFI by Recipe" Description="Dry Matter and As Fed Intake grouped by Recipe" CreatedDT="2013-08-22T16:25:35.113" ModifiedDT="2014-12-11T15:05:54.337" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAACaoM=" ReportVersion="2" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select ReportDate, PenNumber , PenName , sum(AF) as TotalAF , case when avg(PenCount) = 0 then 0 else sum(AF) / avg(PenCount) end as WAvgAFHd , sum(AF * DMPct) as TotalDM , case when Avg(PenCount) = 0 then 0 else sum(DMPct * AF) / Avg(PenCount) end as WAvgDMHd , sum(case when AF < 0 then AF else 0 end) as TotalWBAF , sum(case when AF >= 0 then AF else 0 end) as TotalDropAF , sum(DMPct * case when AF < 0 then AF else 0 end) as TotalWBDM , sum(case when AF >= 0 then DMPct * AF else 0 end) as TotalDropDM , avg(PenCount) as AvgPenCount , RecipeName from ( select case when p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID then 1 else -1 end * dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) as AF, convert(date, it.TransactionDT) as ReportDate, l.LocationName as PenName, p.PenNumber as PenNumber, it.DMPct, l.LocationName, case when p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID then 0 else 1 end as IsWeighback, (select top 1 [Count] from PenCountChange where PenGID = p.PenGID and InventoryItemType = 3 and CreatedDT <= it.TransactionDT order by CreatedDT desc) as PenCount, (select top 1 r.RecipeName from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join Recipe r on r.RecipeGID = coalesce(fsm.ActualRecipeGID, fsm.OverrideRecipeGID, fsm.PlanRecipeGID) where fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID = it.TransactionSourceGID) as RecipeName from InventoryTransaction it join Ingredient i on i.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Pen p on p.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID or p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = p.LocationGID join Company c on c.CompanyGID = l.CompanyGID ) p group by ReportDate, PenName, PenNumber, RecipeName</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
